{"tid":1995601,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"amd cpu&gpu 討論post #44 睇#1&有時間幫手填表","createTime":"2020-04-30T11:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T12:57:26.000Z","uid":195348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e00056d9c28d9768ae46b16ef1b7ed25fd2179bc","tid":1995601,"uid":195348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎來到 AMD CPU&amp;GPU 討論POST</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點提醒</span></span></strong><br />\n如果要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">換新cpu</span></strong>/<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新散熱器</span></strong>/<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拆原裝散熱器</span></strong> 請<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開機預熱/直接燒機10分鐘</span></strong>再處理 否則出現<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拔劍/彎針腳</span></strong>情況 另外原廠散熱器負帶的散熱膏有著<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">水泥散熱膏</span></strong>花名 有需要上新散熱膏 <br />\n<br />\n大家都知買AMD CPU &amp; GPU都有送Game Code既 promotion  所以要了解清楚兌換遊戲Code流程  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 收到產品即上代理登記產品資料<br />\n2. 等待代理發送遊戲Code<br />\n3. 入AMD Award登記&amp;兌換<br />\n<br />\n買AMD Ryzen CPU前<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請留意粒U係邊間代理</span></strong>  <br />\n<strong>Xander</strong>&amp;<strong>VST</strong>為<strong>正式代理</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>Gigabyte Bios內調整PBO Boost &amp; Fclk freq請去AMD Overclock揾！！！！！</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新手入門</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/19UlC9tYn59JPk30TcScZZqgty39eGGcZFJVdBcJs_H4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%